DISCIPLINARY DOCKET

93-1828. In re Resignation of Steffen.

On response to court’s order of September 23, 1994 regarding payment of board costs. Respondent is found in contempt, but the order is placed in the file.

*1460Moyer, C.J., P.E. Sweeney and Cook, JJ., would find respondent in contempt and refer this cause to the Attorney General for collection proceedings.
